    "name": "Custom Hyperlink Hover Color (Global)",
    "description": "Hyperlink Hover Styling for ALL WebPages.  This style improves page navigation and element focus, for pages without their own form of mouse-hovering.\r\n\r\n\r\nFeatures:\r\n- Orange href hover highlight text (customizable)\r\n- Will only show up on pages that don't already have a hover color.  In the case of an orange background, or custom sites.   If you want this style to show up no matter what, add !important between the last 0 and the : in the code.\r\n\r\nIntegrates with Style 8772\r\n\r\nChangelog:\r\n- Initial Release",
